<Page title="About Satori" description="EOS Coaches & Fractional Leaders in Asia. Built by Operators, Not Just Advisors.">
  <Hero
    title="We're on a mission to empower founders and entrepreneurs to build thriving businesses and achieve lasting success."
    subtitle="Built by Operators, Not Just Advisors"
    eyebrow="About Team Satori"
    image="/images/heroes/hero-about.jpg"
    description="You won't find generic consultants here. Our team includes entrepreneurs who have built and scaled businesses to exit and understand the pains of what it takes to get a company to ever higher levels of performance and returns."
  />

  <!-- Why Clients Choose Us -->
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-site">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-12">
        <span class="eyebrow mb-3 block">Why clients choose us</span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-4xl mb-6">We&rsquo;ve Been Where You Are</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-800 leading-relaxed">
          We&rsquo;ve been in the trenches in our own businesses, and we&rsquo;ve worked alongside founder-led companies across Southeast and East Asia &mdash; from tech startups in Vietnam to family-run firms in Singapore and the Philippines.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-6">We&rsquo;ve seen what happens when:</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-16">
        <div class="card p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-error" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-2.5L13.732 4c-.77-.833-1.964-.833-2.732 0L4.082 16.5c-.77.833.192 2.5 1.732 2.5z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-800 font-bold">Leadership is misaligned</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-600 mt-2">Different priorities pulling the team in different directions</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-error" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-800 font-bold">Hiring systems are overwhelmed</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-600 mt-2">Growing faster than your people processes can support</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-error" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-800 font-bold">No clear strategy to anchor decisions</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-600 mt-2">Chasing opportunities without a framework to evaluate them</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-error" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4" /></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-800 font-bold">Accountability stays murky</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-600 mt-2">Teams grow but nobody owns the outcomes</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-neutral-800 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mb-16">
        We don&rsquo;t offer one-size-fits-all solutions. We embed where we&rsquo;re needed &mdash; whether in ops, finance, people services, or execution &mdash; and we help you get from where you are to where you want to be.
      </p>

      <!-- What Makes Us Different -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-4xl">What Makes Us Different</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Operators, Not Consultants</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">We&rsquo;ve built and scaled our own businesses. We bring founder experience, not textbook theory.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Certified Methodologies</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">EOS&reg;, Profit First, Gallup&reg; Strengths, Kolbe&trade; &mdash; proven frameworks, not ad-hoc advice.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Embedded, Not Advisory</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">We don&rsquo;t hand you a deck and leave. We work alongside your team until the systems are running.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Regional Expertise</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Deep understanding of Southeast and East Asia&rsquo;s business culture, talent markets, and growth dynamics.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-purple-50" id="team">
    <div class="container-site">
      <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-4xl text-center mb-16">Meet Our Team</h2>

      <!-- Leadership -->
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        {leadership.map((member) => (
          <TeamMember {...member} />
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- EOS Implementers -->
      <h3 class="text-xl text-center mb-8 text-neutral-600">EOS Implementers</h3>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-16">
        {eosImplementers.map((member) => (
          <TeamMember {...member} />
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- Operations -->
      <h3 class="text-xl text-center mb-8 text-neutral-600">Operations & Support</h3>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        {operations.map((member) => (
          <TeamMember {...member} />
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTA title="Let's Build the Systems That Match Your Vision" />
</Page>
